Class AdobeBehanceSDKAbstractPublishOptions

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.adobe.creativesdk.behance.AdobeBehanceSDKAbstractPublishOptions
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdobeBehanceAddProjectWorkflowOptions, AdobeBehanceSDKPublishProjectOptions

    public class AdobeBehanceSDKAbstractPublishOptions
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents options for publishing Behance Project and Work in Progress. This is the base class for AdobeBehanceSDKPublishProjectOptions class.
